1.download/clone this repo (kalakriti chatbot)

2.Install Backend Dependencies
Go to the backend folder and install the required packages:

cd backend
npm install

3.Install Frontend Dependencies
Next, go to the frontend folder and install the frontend dependencies:

cd ../frontend
npm install

4.Run the Backend
In the backend folder, start the backend server:

cd backend
nodemon index.js

5.Run the Frontend
In a separate terminal, start the frontend:

cd frontend
npm run dev

Access the Website
Once both the backend and frontend are running, you can access the website at:

http://localhost:5173
